commitResults.messageTitle: Create 'tasklist.txt' for storing tasks to hard disk
commitResults.messageBody:
The tasks are stored in an array.

Storing tasks in an array doesn't save the tasks when the program reruns.

Change the storing of tasks into a .txt file instead.

commitResults.messageTitle: Update bye() method and load 'tasklist.txt' to 'tasks' arraylist
commitResults.messageBody:
Tasks are not stored in hard disk i.e 'tasklist.txt', stored in 'tasks' arraylist instead.

Task list progress is lost everytime the program is rerun.

Progress is loaded at the start into 'tasks' arraylist from 'tasklist.txt' and saved into 'tasklist.txt' when 'bye' command is entered.
